219
00:13:09,880 --> 00:13:10,440
Mom! Mom!

220
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:11,120
I'm coming down now.

221
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:12,240
Let's pick up the package together.

222
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,560
It's okay, no need.

223
00:13:13,560 --> 00:13:14,280
It's not heavy.

224
00:13:14,760 --> 00:13:15,320
It's fine.

225
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:16,200
I'm hanging up now.

226
00:13:17,160 --> 00:13:17,840
Quick, quick!

227
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:18,560
My mom's back.

228
00:13:18,560 --> 00:13:19,520
She is downstairs.

229
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:38,880
Madam, let me help you.

230
00:13:39,880 --> 00:13:40,640
Thank you.

231
00:13:47,060 --> 00:13:47,840
