and so polite too.

245
00:14:20,160 --> 00:14:21,560
I wonder which girl

246
00:14:21,560 --> 00:14:23,080
is lucky enough to have you.

247
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:24,640
- Mengmeng.
- Mom.

248
00:14:25,520 --> 00:14:26,200
Bai Lian.

249
00:14:28,760 --> 00:14:29,800
Boyfriend?

250
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:34,000
He...

251
00:14:34,880 --> 00:14:36,120
