263
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:50,880
He seems busy.

264
00:14:50,880 --> 00:14:51,640
Hold this.

265
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:52,440
Not busy at all.

266
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:54,000
